    <span id="MainContent_FeatLabel"><h2><h1 class="title">Critical Feats</h1></h2><b>Description </b> <b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/pathfinderRPG/v5748btpy88yj" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 112</i></a><br />Critical feats modify the effects of a critical hit by inflicting an additional condition on the victim of the critical hit. Characters without the Critical Mastery feat can only apply the effects of one critical feat to an individual critical hit. Characters with multiple critical feats can decide which feat to apply after the critical hit has been confirmed.<br /><br /></span>
    <span id="MainContent_FeatLabel2"><div style="font-size:12px"><i>*combat feat</i><br /><i><sup>⊤</sup>armor mastery feat</i><br /><i><sup>⊤⊤</sup>shield mastery feat</i><br /><i><sup>⊤⊤⊤</sup>weapon mastery feat</i><br /><br /></div></span>
